      "title": "Yupun's first shop was a success",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Sri Lanka's Supuri sprint champion Yupun Abeykoon, who played in a qualifying match of the 100m men's race at the Commonwealth Games held in England, managed to win the first place.",
        "Yupun completed the race in 10.06 seconds and thus qualified for the semi-final."
